1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,580
Your GPS would be wrong by two kilometers every single day.

2
00:00:03,580 --> 00:00:05,280
Without a theory, a bored patent clerk

3
00:00:05,280 --> 00:00:07,560
wrote for fun in 1905.

4
00:00:07,560 --> 00:00:10,000
The blue dot on your map exists because Einstein

5
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:13,200
got curious about light between stamping paperwork,

6
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:15,720
which makes the real question even stranger.

7
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:17,440
Where did all the Einsteins go?
